title: Fiji Tourism Revenues
description: Tourism Revenues in Fiji increased to 337.50 FJD Million in the second quarter of 2022 from 109.40 FJD Million in the first quarter of 2022. Tourism Revenues in Fiji averaged 343.70 FJD Million from 2012 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 648.90 FJD Million in the third quarter of 2018 and a record low of 1.20 FJD Million in the third quarter of 2021. This page provides - Fiji Tourism Revenues- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Fiji Bureau of Statistics
